_sText:
A Remake of "zm_lila_sethenHD"


Background:
This version of the map introduces a vivid theme that gives color to the overdone lila panic map. The map has a variety of colors that coordinates each room with it's unique theme.

Support:
Cubemaps, Ammo boxes, Max Spawnpoints, Optimization
